Coldwell Banker High Country Realty - Blue Ridge

data.description: This cozy, short-term rental-friendly home just 11 minutes from downtown Blairsville beckons you offering you move-in-ready features plus 1 acre of usable land with seasonal mountain views. Enjoy a main-floor primary suite that includes closet laundry (stacked) and access to your own deck where you can enjoy early-morning coffee or late-night stargazing. The LR/DR includes a propane fireplace/heater. Between those rooms and the kitchen are French doors that lead out to the screened deck, your new happy place. Upstairs is a loft bedroom suite and barn door-style access to the private deck. Fenced-in yard, aluminum carport, crawlspace, and covered carport-style storage in back of home. Propane (powers FP heater & dryer), septic, and public water. This home would make a great investment property for short-term rentals. Or, use it as the occasional getaway spot. Either way, act fastGat this price, this one won't last long!
